---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — MailPilot"
  description="How MailPilot handles your data."
>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="meta">Last updated: 2026-07-02</p>

  <p>MailPilot is an affiliate marketing site. We earn commissions when you click certain links on this site and sign up for the products we recommend. This is how the site is funded.</p>

  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Anonymous page views and traffic source data via Google Analytics 4. We do not collect personally identifiable information through analytics.</li>
    <li><strong>Email (if you contact us):</strong> If you send us an email, we keep the message and your reply address long enough to respond. We don't add you to any marketing list.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What we don't collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>No account registration required to browse</li>
    <li>No payment data ever touches our servers</li>
    <li>No third-party advertising networks beyond Google Analytics</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>Google Analytics sets cookies for anonymous traffic measurement. Affiliate programs may set cookies to track referrals. You can disable cookies in your browser without breaking the site.</p>
</BaseLayout>